org.relationlearn.util.io.OutputGenerator

  • Packages that use OutputGenerator 
    Package Description
    org.relationlearn.util.io
    Provides facilites for the parsing of input data and the generation of output data in multiple formats.

    • Uses of OutputGenerator in org.relationlearn.util.io

      Classes in org.relationlearn.util.io that implement OutputGenerator 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DLVFileGenerator
      OutputGenerator implementation which generates a group of files in the ASPARTIX AF extension language format, which can be used for argument reasoning argumnet reasoning using tools such as DLV.
      class  DOTFileGenerator
      OutputGenerator implementation which generates a group of files in the DOT language format for graph representation using tools such as GraphViz.
      class  XMLFileGenerator
      OutputGenerator implementation which generates a file in the NoDE format, using an XML stream writer.
